data.name: label3.Text
data.value: A skin care treatment that exfoliates skin. A microdermabrasion machine that uses a crystal tip wand and suction are used to help with light exfoliation. This method allows for thorough cleaning of clogged pores and improved skin texture. Custom products are used with each service to best suit your individual needs.

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: A skin care treatment that consists of using a 10-gauge scalpel to gently scrape off the top layer of skin and vellous hair. Once finished a smoother softer complexion is achieved. Dermaplane is included with a full facial. Ideal treatment before special events or photo shoots. Allows for better application of make-up.
